// Soft fork: actl stands on act but needs a pause-barrier hook in pkg/runner
// that upstream does not expose. We track a pinned act release in third_party/act
// and keep our patch minimal. Flip this to github.com/ruzmuh/act once the fork is
// pushed; drop it entirely if the hook lands upstream.
replace github.com/nektos/act => ./third_party/act
